articles.title: Australia woman rescued after getting stuck between boulders - BBC.com
articles.description: The woman spent seven hours upside down between the boulders, with only her feet visible to rescuers.
articles.content:
The woman slipped into a three-metre crevice
A young woman spent hours trapped upside down after slipping between two boulders as she tried to retrieve her mobile phone during a hike in Australia.
